e solution for investors seeking yield and attractive returns” about hamilton lane hamilton lane is an independent alternative investment management firm providing innovative private markets solutions to sophisticated investors around the world the firm has been dedicated to private markets investing for more than two decades and currently has more than  employees operating in offices throughout the us europe asia latin america and the middle east with more than  billion in total assets under management and supervision hamilton lane offers a full range of investment products and services that enable clients to participate in the private markets asset class on a global and customized basis  as of march    hamilton lane announces senior promotions in london « previous  hamilton lanes latest global fundoffunds closes above target next »   philadelphialondonmunichsydneyhong kongrio de janeirosan franciscosan diegonew yorkmiamitel avivtokyolas vegasseoul home              terms of use              site index copyright   hamilton lane all rights reserved hamilton lane holds final close on latest fundoffunds careerssubmit investment opportunitycontact usclient login aboutinvestment approachinvestment solutionsmedia roominvestor relations media roomfirm newsarticlesupcoming eventsmarket overviewvideospremium content newsvideosfirm newsarticles hamilton lane holds final close on latest fundoffunds  bala cynwyd penn  – hamilton lane advisors llc “hamilton lane” a leading global private markets asset management firm today announced the final closing of hamilton lane private equity fund viii lp the “fund” a global and diversified private equity fundoffunds originally targeting  million the fund received strong interest from the institutional investor community exceeding its target to close on  million “despite the consolidation happening in the fundsoffunds market today we believe the demand for fund viii is a testament to hamilton lane’s highly selective investment process and track record within this sector” said mario giannini chief executive officer of hamilton lane “we are pleased to share the news of the final close of our most recent fundof funds thanks to support from a diverse group of both new and existing hamilton lane investors including public pension funds tafthartley pension plans endowments foundations and other institutions” “with an emphasis on thoughtful portfolio construction the fund is designed to provide investors with an opportunity for both short and longterm performance through a strategic blend of exposure across strategies vintage years and geographies” said jackie rantanen principal in the product management group at hamilton lane hamilton lane has been managing fundsoffunds strategies since  and seeks to provide access to the top echelon of funds worldwide through its robust platform leveraging the firm’s global presence and rigorous due diligence process the fund represents a continuation of hamilton lane’s tailored fundsoffunds approach to provide investors with a balanced portfolio of private market investments about hamilton lane hamilton lane is an independent alternative investment management firm providing innovative private markets solutions to sophisticated investors around the world the firm has been dedicated to private markets investing for more than two decades and currently has more than  employees operating in offices throughout the us london hong kong rio de janeiro tel aviv and tokyo with over  billion in total assets under management and supervision hamilton lane offers a full range of investment products and services that enable clients to participate in the private markets asset class on a global and customized basis the firm has been named an inc  fastestgrowing company and a “best places to work in money management by pensions  investments for more information please visit wwwhamiltonlanecom  as of december   contact kate dillon prosek partners   ext  kdillonprosekcom  principles for re